name: Pink variety
description:
About a women who smhw turns into an obsessive compulsive angel in front of a mirror. For example picking a lipstick color... lets say pink, okay but which pink! Some say that lipstick is just a waste of time but no, there are darker pink, lighter pink, not all pink match my skin colour, etc. Well, our mind is complex and smhw works  in a weird way, but it makes us beautiful (inside and outside). Complexly Beautiful Being that spend a loooooong time in the mirror. 

This work is inspired by Jason Ranti's Song titled "Variasi Pink"
